beIN SPORTS 2.original_title: Pafos vs Slavia Praha - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 2.title: Pafos vs Slavia Praha - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 2.desc: Pafos versus Slavia Prague will be the first ever European Cup/UEFA Champions League match played between teams from Cyprus and Czechia. This will be the first time Pafos have faced an opponent from Czechia in European competition, while Slavia Prague have only faced a Cypriot side in one previous campaign, being eliminated by APOEL Nicosia in qualifying for the 2017-18 UEFA Champions League.

beIN SPORTS 2.original_title: Napoli vs Chelsea - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 2.title: Napoli vs Chelsea - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 2.desc: The only previous meetings between Napoli and Chelsea came in the 2011-12 UEFA Champions League, with the Blues eliminating the Italian side in the Round of 16 in that edition. Chelsea have only won one of their last nine UEFA Champions League away games against Italian sides  – a 2-0 victory at Milan in October 2022 – while losing six of the last seven. The most recent of those came this season, losing at Atalanta on MD6, despite having taken the lead.

beIN SPORTS 2.original_title: Monaco vs Juventus - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 2.title: Monaco vs Juventus - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 2.desc: Monaco have only won one of their six games against Juventus in European competition, a 3-2 triumph in April 1998. They have failed to win all four meetings  this century, failing to score in three of those. This will be the first meeting between Monaco and Juventus since the semi-finals of the 2016-17 UEFA Champions League, where the Old Lady progressed to the final after winning both legs.

beIN SPORTS 3.title: Bristol City vs Derby County - EFL - English Football League  SkyBet - Championship 2025/2026
beIN SPORTS 3.desc: Bristol City have won their last four home league games against Derby, keeping a clean sheet in each of the last three. Derby manager John Eustace has lost three of his four away matches against Bristol City in the Championship, including the only time he has lost a game by 5+ goals as a manager in the competition.

beIN SPORTS 3.original_title: Nottingham Forest vs Ferencváros - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 3.title: Nottingham Forest vs Ferencváros - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 3.desc: This is the first meeting between Nottingham Forest and Ferencváros and Forest’s first game against a Hungarian side. Ferencváros have lost six of their nine away major European matches in England, with their one win coming at Liverpool in January 1968.

beIN SPORTS 3.original_title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 3.title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 3.desc: Despite having a combined 792 European Cup/UEFA Champions League matches between them, these teams have only met three times across the two competitions, and not since the 1964-65 quarter-finals.  Benfica have won two of the previous three meetings between themselves and Real Madrid, while their one defeat came in the second leg of the 1964-65 quarter-finals ; a tie they still progressed from 6-3 on aggregate.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Despite having a combined 792 European Cup/UEFA Champions League matches between them, these teams have only met three times across the two competitions, and not since the 1964-65 quarter-finals.  Benfica have won two of the previous three meetings between themselves and Real Madrid, while their one defeat came in the second leg of the 1964-65 quarter-finals ; a tie they still progressed from 6-3 on aggregate.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Ligue 1 Weekly Review - 2025/2026
beIN SPORTS 1.title: Ligue 1 Weekly Review - 2025/2026
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Each Ligue 1 Match week is condensed into a 52-minute highlights show. Every game, goal, penalty, red card and everything in between is squeezed into an action-packed hour to ensure no football fan misses a kick across the game season.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: AFCON 2025 Senegal - The Champions
beIN SPORTS 1.title: AFCON 2025 Senegal - The Champions
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Senegal were crowned champions of Africa for the second time in their history after edging hosts Morocco 1–0 after extra time in a gripping Africa Cup of Nations (AFCON) final in Rabat.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Barcelona vs Copenhagen - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: Barcelona vs Copenhagen - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Barcelona and Copenhagen’s only two previous meetings came in the group stage of the 2010-11 UEFA Champions League – Barcelona won 2-0 in the home fixture thanks to a Lionel Messi brace, before drawing 1-1 in the reverse fixture in Denmark. Copenhagen didn’t win any of their first 15 matches against Spanish teams in European competition, yet won their most recent one, versus Villarreal on MD6 of this season’s UEFA Champions League.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Despite having a combined 792 European Cup/UEFA Champions League matches between them, these teams have only met three times across the two competitions, and not since the 1964-65 quarter-finals.  Benfica have won two of the previous three meetings between themselves and Real Madrid, while their one defeat came in the second leg of the 1964-65 quarter-finals ; a tie they still progressed from 6-3 on aggregate.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Paris Saint-Germain vs Newcastle United - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: Paris Saint-Germain vs Newcastle United - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Paris SG and Newcastle’s only previous meetings came in the 2023-24 UEFA Champions League – the two sides drew their meeting at the Parc des Princes, after Eddie Howe’s side had won 4-1 in the first game at St. James’ Park. This will be Newcastle’s 10th away game against a French side in Europe, while they have only managed one victory from the previous nine : 4-0 v Sochaux in the UEFA Cup in November 2004.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Liverpool vs Qarabağ  - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: Liverpool vs Qarabağ  - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: Liverpool and Qarabag will meet for the first time in European competition – all three previous meetings between sides from England and Azerbaijan in the UEFA Champions League have been between Qarabag and Chelsea. Qarabag lost seven of their first eight meetings with English sides in Europe, but they did avoid defeat in the most recent one in the UEFA Champions League this season.

beIN SPORTS 5.desc: This will be the fifth AFC Champions League Elite meeting between Al-Ahli and Nasaf, with Nasaf’s only win coming in their most recent such game on 2 March 2016 ; Al-Ahli’s most recent game in the competition against Uzbek opposition was a 2-1 win over Pakhtakor Tashkent on 20 May 2019, a win here will see them win two consecutive such games for the first time in competition history.
